These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, snake, dog, turtle, pony, frog
House: victorian, ranch-style, wooden, cape-cod, art-deco, craftsman, tower
 1. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the frog##2
 2. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 3. the art-deco house is on the right of the tower house##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is between the wooden house and the art-deco house##2
 5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 6. the ranch-style house is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the victorian house is between the cape-cod house and the wooden house##2
 8. the ranch-style house is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the wooden house##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Pet   | dog | cat | frog | hamster    | snake | turtle   | pony    |
| House         | craftsman  | ranch-style   | cape-cod | victorian | wooden   | tower | art-deco |

