.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, november, february, march, september, may, october
House: gothic-revival, tower, cape-cod, victorian, futuristic, wooden, craftsman
1. the wooden house is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in may and the wooden house##2
3. the tower house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle##1
6. the futuristic house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the victorian house##1
9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Birthday          | september | february | may | november | october | january      | march  |
| House   | wooden | victorian  | craftsman     | cape-cod     | futuristic  | gothic-revival | tower |

