.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, december, november, march, august, june, september
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, thriller, satire, martial-arts, mystery, musical, romance
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 8. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Birthday   | september | august | february | december   | march | november | june |
| Movie-Genre           | mystery | musical     | thriller     | satire | martial-arts   | zombie   | romance    |

